{
  "stem": "27509.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the-- the banks that used to do it, who came into the existence, were the people who used to discount those long-term promissory notes to give the holders ready cash with which to pay wages and to-- and to make ends meet until such time that the cycle turned around in full.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then the next-- the next product came along.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the new promissory notes came into-- and then you start praying every day that-- that by the time that the-- the date is due that they will find the money there to pay for it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the-- and then, of course, there was a great, a very developed social and political activity.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every aspect of-- of life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and it was all voluntary, paramedical and medical in the Jewish hospital and-- and-- and the different parties and different institutions and clubs and [INAUDIBLE] vote and schools and so on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was all Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was all Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And culturally?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And culturally-- culturally, it was a-- it was a-- a-- a Garden of Eden.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's why when I first arrived here, from the Jewish point of view, I arrived in a desert.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I arrived in a desert because one of the first questions that they asked me when I arrived in-- in this country, and I was at [POLISH] home, the first question that I asked them, how many Jewish day schools have you got here?",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the answer was none.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So within 48 hours of my arrival in Australia, I knew what I had to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think I have mentioned it in passing before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were aware.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't not be aware because first of all, there was a press.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was already a radio.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
